+    `Skill source records: ${result.skillIntake.recordsBuilt} built, ${result.skillIntake.admittedRecordCount} admitted, ${result.skillIntake.referenceOrBlockedRecordCount} reference/blocked`,
+    `Formal skill candidates: ${result.skillIntake.formalSkillCandidateCount} candidates, ${result.skillIntake.admittedFormalSkillCount} admitted, ${result.skillIntake.formalSkillBundleCount} bundles`,
+    `Runtime dispatched skills: ${result.skillIntake.runtimeDispatchedSkillCount} (${result.skillIntake.formalSkillRuntimeDebt} formal candidates not dispatched)`,
+    `Declared-only skill debt: ${result.skillIntake.declaredOnlyBefore} -> ${result.skillIntake.declaredOnlyAfter}`,
